# ROS Data Acquisition Driver for 3DM-GX3-15 IMU module (Single Byte Protocol)

This program is from Nathan Michael's original ROS driver for the Lord Corporation Microstrain 3DM GX3 15,25 IMU 

Adding and compiling:

1. cd ~/ros2_ws/src

2. git clone https://github.com/jimin3722/3dm_gx3_15_ros.git

3. cd ..

4. colcon_build 


Usage:

ros2 run imu_3dm_gx3 imu_3dm_gx3 port:=/dev/ttyACM0 decimation:=2

imu_data_rate = 1000/decimation HZ

